{"sn2.14:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 2.14 ","sn2.14:0.2":"2. Anathapindikavagga ","sn2.14:0.3":"Nandanasutta ","sn2.14:1.1":"Ekamantam thito kho nandano devaputto bhagavantam gathaya ajjhabhasi: ","sn2.14:2.1":"“Pucchami tam gotama bhuripanna, ","sn2.14:2.2":"Anavatam bhagavato nanadassanam; ","sn2.14:2.3":"Kathamvidham silavantam vadanti, ","sn2.14:2.4":"Kathamvidham pannavantam vadanti; ","sn2.14:2.5":"Kathamvidho dukkhamaticca iriyati, ","sn2.14:2.6":"Kathamvidham devata pujayanti”ti. ","sn2.14:3.1":"“Yo silava pannava bhavitatto, ","sn2.14:3.2":"Samahito jhanarato satima; ","sn2.14:3.3":"Sabbassa soka vigata pahina, ","sn2.14:3.4":"Khinasavo antimadehadhari. ","sn2.14:4.1":"Tathavidham silavantam vadanti, ","sn2.14:4.2":"Tathavidham pannavantam vadanti; ","sn2.14:4.3":"Tathavidho dukkhamaticca iriyati, ","sn2.14:4.4":"Tathavidham devata pujayanti”ti. "}